 f_Z(z)=\int_{0}^{\infty} \frac{1}{t} f_Y(\frac{z}{t}\big)f_X\left(t\right)dt+ \int_{-\infty}^{0} \frac{-1}{t} f_Y(\frac{z}{t}\big) f_X\left(t\right)dt 
 =\int_{-\infty}^{\infty} \frac{1}{|t|} f_X\left(t\right)f_Y\left(\frac{z}{t}\right)dt 
 \begin{array}{|c|}\hline\\ \color{#ff0000}{\large\quad% {\cal P}\left(Z\right) = \int_{-\infty}^{\infty} {\rm P_{X}}\left(X\right)\,{\rm P_{Y}}\left(Z \over X\right)\, \,{{\rm d}X \over \left\vert X\right\vert} \quad} \\ \\ \hline \end{array} 
